'''琉森節慶管弦樂團'''（{{lang-en|'''Lucerne Festival Orchestra'''}}），亦稱為「'''琉森音乐节管弦乐团'''」，是為瑞士[[琉森音樂節|琉森音樂節]][[Ad_hoc|特設]]的節慶樂團。

== 背景 ==
=== 早期 ===
樂團的歷史最早可溯自1938年，當時由[[阿图罗·托斯卡尼尼|阿图罗·托斯卡尼尼]]指揮了創團首場演出<ref name="Hilferty">{{cite news | url=http://www.playbillarts.com/features/article/7005.html | title=Lucerne in the Sky with Diamonds | work=Playbill Arts | author=Robert Hilferty | date=2007-09-01 | accessdate=2007-09-01 | archive-date=2017-12-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215001105/http://www.playbillarts.com/features/article/7005.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。自1943年至1993年解散為止，樂團主要的組成是瑞士本土音樂家，之後重整的樂團則以[[古斯塔夫·马勒青年管弦乐团|马勒青年乐团]]、[[歐盟青年管弦樂團|歐洲共同體管弦樂團]]的團員為主<ref>Palmer, Peter, "First Performances: Lucerne Festival" (January 1996).  ''Tempo'' (New Ser.), '''195''': {{pp.|25-26}}.</ref>。

=== 阿巴多時代 ===
2000年之後，義大利指揮家[[克劳迪奥·阿巴多|克劳迪奥·阿巴多]]的加入為樂團注入一劑強心針，他帶來{{link-en|馬勒室內樂團|Mahler Chamber Orchestra}}的團員作為骨幹，並廣邀各大職業樂團首席與其成員加入演出，包括了[[柯爾亞·布拉赫|柯爾亞·布拉赫]]、{{link-de|沃爾夫拉姆·克里斯特|Wolfram Christ (Musiker)}}、{{link-en|米里賈姆·康岑|Mirijam Contzen}}、{{link-en|荻慕特·波朋|Diemut Poppen}}、[[娜塔莉娅·格里戈里耶夫娜·古特曼|娜塔莉娅·古特曼]]、{{link-de|延斯·彼得·邁因茨|Jens Peter Maintz}}、{{link-nl|賈奎斯·榮恩|Jacques Zoon}}、{{link-de|萊因霍爾德·弗里德里希|Reinhold Friedrich}}、{{link-de|斯特凡·多爾|Stefan Dohr}}、{{link-de|阿萊西奧·阿列格里尼|Alessio Allegrini}}、{{link-en|馬克·坦伯頓 (音樂家)|Mark Templeton (trombonist)|馬克·坦伯頓}}、法蘭茨·巴托洛梅、阿洛以斯·波施、{{link-en|艾曼紐·帕胡德|Emmanuel Pahud}}、{{link-de|阿爾布雷希特·梅爾|Albrecht Mayer}}、{{link-de|斯特凡·施瓦格特|Stefan Schweigert}}等一線樂團的重要成員，以及萨宾娜·迈耶合奏團、[[阿班·貝爾格四重奏團|阿班·貝爾格弦樂四重奏]]、[[哈根四重奏團|哈根四重奏團]]等室內樂團體皆響應了這一號召。除了上述的演奏家外，阿巴多亦會親自邀請與其有良好互動的音樂家加入，主要來自其合作融洽的柏林愛樂、[[伦敦交响乐团|伦敦交响]]、[[维也纳爱乐乐团|维也纳爱乐]]等樂團<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/arts/main.jhtml?xml=/arts/2007/08/14/bmlucerne114.xml | title= Electrifying artistry: Lucerne Festival Orchestra | work=[[每日电讯报|Telegraph]] | author=Geoffrey Norris | date=2007-08-14 | accessdate=2007-08-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://arts.guardian.co.uk/critic/review/0,,1856380,00.html | title=Lucerne Festival Orchestra/Abbado | work=[[衛報|The Guardian]] | author=Tom Service  date=2006-08-23 | accessdate=2007-08-31}}</ref>，可以說是由阿巴多親自精挑細選的一支「精兵」樂團<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/08/26/arts/26iht-loomis.html?_r=2 |title=Loomis, George "Commanding, time and again", ''New York Times'' (2009-08-25) |access-date=2021-02-04 |archive-date=2018-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805160726/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/08/26/arts/26iht-loomis.html?_r=2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

樂團的成員會在每年8月初抵達琉森，展開為期三週左右的音樂節行程，當中約有10天用於排練。在接下來的音樂節開幕演出中，他們是當然的揭幕團體<ref>{{cite news | url=http://arts.guardian.co.uk/fridayreview/story/0,,1327019,00.html | title=Follow the leader | work=The Guardian | author=Stephen Everson | date=2004-10-15 | accessdate=2007-08-31 | archive-date=2008-10-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011075321/http://arts.guardian.co.uk/fridayreview/story/0,,1327019,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。阿巴多鼓勵樂團以室內樂的方式聆聽彼此，同時亦保有管弦樂團的厚度<ref>{{cite news | url=http://music.guardian.co.uk/classical/livereviews/story/0,,2148331,00.html | title=Lucerne FO/ Abbado Konzertsaal | work=The Guardian | author=Tom Service | date=2007-08-14 | accessdate=2007-08-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://music.guardian.co.uk/proms2007/story/0,,2153754,00.html | title=The maestro | work=The Guardian | author=Tom Service | date=2007-08-22 | accessdate=2007-08-31 | archive-date=2008-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706093857/http://music.guardian.co.uk/proms2007/story/0,,2153754,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。弦樂部門的座次先後，是由首席們與阿巴多共同討論議定的。在正式的團練之前，各聲部亦會舉行自主練習，以期提高彩排效率<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/30/arts/music/30waki.html?pagewanted=all | title=Not Just Another Pickup Band | work=New York Times | author=Daniel J. Wakin | date=2007-09-30 | accessdate=2007-10-11 | archive-date=2018-08-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805114519/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/30/arts/music/30waki.html?pagewanted=all | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2003年，阿巴多率領新生的琉森節慶樂團在音樂節上亮相，之後他們曾在2005年前往羅馬駐紮，2006年的東京行則是他們首次前往海外演出。2007年8月，樂團首登[[逍遥音乐会|逍遥音乐会]]，演出[[古斯塔夫·馬勒|馬勒]][[第3號交響曲_(馬勒)|第3號交響曲]]，大受好評<ref>{{cite news | url=http://music.guardian.co.uk/proms2007/story/0,,2155410,00.html | title=Lucerne Festival Orchestra/Abbado (review of Prom 51, 2007) | work=The Guardian | author=Andrew Clements | date=2007-08-24 | accessdate=2007-08-31 | archive-date=2008-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080705135937/http://music.guardian.co.uk/proms2007/story/0,,2155410,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/live_reviews/article2315132.ece | title=Proms: Lucerne FO/Abbado | newspaper=The Times | author=Richard Morrison | date=2007-08-24 | accessdate=2007-08-31 | archive-date=2011-05-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110517050630/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/music/live_reviews/article2315132.ece | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/3492dfce-51d8-11dc-8779-0000779fd2ac.html | title=Lucerne Festival Orchestra, Royal Albert Hall, London | work=Financial Times | author=Richard Fairman | date=2007-08-24 | accessdate=2007-08-31}}</ref>。原先樂團計畫9月續訪紐約[[卡内基大厅|卡内基厅]]<ref name="Hilferty"/>，因阿巴多的健康因素而取消<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/7025.html | title=Conductor Claudio Abbado Withdraws from Carnegie Hall Season Openers Next Month | work=Playbill Arts | author=Matthew Westphal | date=2007-09-06 | accessdate=2007-09-07 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924093606/http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/7025.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/07/arts/music/07abba.html | title=Abbado, Ill, Cancels Appearances | work=New York Times | author=Daniel J. Wakin | date=2007-09-07 | accessdate=2007-09-07 | archive-date=2019-08-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812060736/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/09/07/arts/music/07abba.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>{{notetag|相關的演出由[[皮埃尔·布莱兹|皮埃尔·布莱兹]]、[[大衛·羅伯森_(指揮)|大衛·羅伯森]]代為指揮<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/7062.html | title=Boulez Replaces Abbado for Lucerne Festival Orchestra's Third Carnegie Hall Concert | work=Playbill Arts | author=Matthew Westphal | date=2007-09-14 | accessdate=2007-09-15 | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203052/http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/7062.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/7077.html | title=David Robertson Replaces Claudio Abbado for Carnegie Hall's Season Openers | work=Playbill Arts | author=Matthew Westphal | date=2007-09-18 | accessdate=2007-09-19 | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220305/http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/7077.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/05/arts/music/05robe.html | title=Orchestra Adjusts to Guest Baton | newspaper=New York Times | author=Anthony Tommasini | date=2007-10-05 | accessdate=2007-10-11 | archive-date=2018-08-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805114514/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/05/arts/music/05robe.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/08/arts/music/08boul.html | title=Be Meticulous With Mahler, and Sentiment Will Follow | newspaper=New York Times | author=James R. Oestreich | date=2007-10-08 | accessdate=2007-10-11 | archive-date=2018-08-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805114526/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/10/08/arts/music/08boul.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}。

=== 近年活動 ===
阿巴多於2014年1月逝世，該年的琉森音樂節由[[安德里斯·尼尔森斯|安德里斯·尼尔森斯]]代理總監，並指揮了節慶樂團的演出<ref>{{cite press release | url=http://www.lucernefestival.ch/documents/140912_MM_LUCERNEFESTIVAL_in_Summer_2014_final_e.pdf | title=Lucerne Festival in Summer ends with a record capacity of 95% | publisher=Lucerne Festival | date=2014-09-14 | accessdate=2015-08-13 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905233739/http://www.lucernefestival.ch/documents/140912_MM_LUCERNEFESTIVAL_in_Summer_2014_final_e.pdf | archivedate=2015-09-05 }}</ref>。2015年8月，[[里卡多·夏伊|里卡多·夏伊]]成為音樂節正式的音樂總監，其五年的合約期自2016年起算<ref>{{cite press release | url=http://www.lucernefestival.ch/documents/150813_MM_LucerneFestivalOrchestra_d.pdf | title=Riccardo Chailly zum Chefdirigenten des Lucerne Festival Orchestra ernannt | publisher=Lucerne Festival | date=2015-08-13 | accessdate=2015-08-13 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911232935/http://www.lucernefestival.ch/documents/150813_MM_LucerneFestivalOrchestra_d.pdf | archivedate=2015-09-11 }}</ref>。

